name: GameJam (CanTalatyakan)
description: A 3D RTS-JamGame, created in Unity with the High-Definition Renderpipeline using C# (in a timespan of 1week). A Real-time strategy game set in medieval times. You build a city with several workstations to provide enough resources for your villagers and workers to created tools, weapons, and products for building a monument, a wonder of the world, that will surpass time into infinity.
